A Modified Tumor-Node-Metastasis Classification for Primary Operable Colorectal 
Cancer.

Zhang C(1)(2), Mei Z(3)(4), Pei J(1), Abe M(5), Zeng X(6)(7), Huang Q(6)(7), 
Nishiyama K(8), Akimoto N(9), Haruki K(9), Nan H(10)(11), Meyerhardt JA(12), 
