Unanswered questions and future direction in the management of terminal 
breathlessness in patients with cancer.

Mori M(1), Yamaguchi T(2), Matsuda Y(3), Suzuki K(4), Watanabe H(5), Matsunuma 
R(6), Kako J(7), Imai K(8), Usui Y(9), Matsumoto Y(9), Hui D(10), Currow D(11), 
Morita T(12).

Author information:
(1)Palliative Care Team, Seirei Mikatahara General Hospital, Hamamatsu, 
